sequenceDiagram
    participant UI as Host UI or Voice App
    participant Loader as Package Loader
    participant Orch as Orchestrator
    participant Mem as Memory Service
    participant Ctx as Context Providers
    participant Tool as Tool Providers
    participant LLM as Model Clients

    UI->>Loader: Select use-case packages
    Loader->>Ctx: Load prebuilt indexes or local indexes
    Loader->>Tool: Load package tool providers
    Loader-->>UI: Component set ready

    UI->>Orch: User turn
    Orch->>Mem: Recall relevant memory
    Orch->>Ctx: Retrieve use-case context
    Orch->>Tool: Invoke selected tools
    Orch->>LLM: Generate answer from memory, context, tools
    LLM-->>Orch: Answer
    Orch->>Mem: Optional writeback proposal or commit
    Orch-->>UI: Answer, citations/context, tool observations
